issue.title: api/Deploy app and get free domain
issue.body:
Knowing that this app will have to be accessible, we must deploy it in an accessible server with its respective domain.

It has to be done using Google Cloud.

issue.title: client/Get origin from API and pass it to the map
issue.body:
Right now the TripMap component does communicate correctly with the API and gets the date for the route. The ideal would be to implement a call to it and pass it as a query parameters to the map URL.

Also, the Map HTML should get the origin, destination and waypoints from the URL query.
